@startuml JPA Entity Persistence State Machine
[*] --> Transient : Entity instantiated (id is null)

Transient --> Managed : save() called -> entityManager.persist()
Managed --> Managed : fields updated & save() called -> entityManager.merge()

Managed --> Detached : Transaction commits / session closed
Detached --> Managed : save() called -> entityManager.merge()

Managed --> Removed : deleteById() called -> entityManager.remove()
Removed --> [*] : Transaction commits (physical delete)
@enduml
